movie_title: Star Wars: Episode I - The Phantom Menace
title: A wonderful experience, this movie is.
review: This movie is truly great.  It is comparable to the original triology in special effects innovation, humor, adventure, mystery, characters, etc. yet still not any more derivative than a story so closely linked to the originals could be.  I loved the chance to experience a new star wars movie while it was still new.  The energy surrounding this film is contagious and I urge you all to go see it.
